0.6.2.1 (2014-01-22)
	- remove upper bounds on dependencies

0.6.1.0 (2013-08-31)
	- upgraded some dependencies

0.6.0.0
	- removed all overloading for names and text-content
	  (overloading caused many typing problems in applications)

0.5.0.0 (2012-09-25)
	- resolved problems with overloaded string literals
	- fixed benchmarks and tests
	- NOT backwards compatible

0.4.0.3 (2012-09-12)
	- Fixes for GHC 7.6

0.4.0.2 (2011-05-21)
	- Use mconcat instead of 'foldr mappend mempty'
	- Removed dependency on xml-types
